{"tid":543488,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"張建宗指周庭不滿被DQ可入稟　 陳浩天選舉呈請審結逾半年仍未有裁決","createTime":"2018-01-28T14:27:53.000Z","updateTime":"2018-01-29T03:18:47.000Z","uid":79563,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"1f6c716801ee01d38e84ac1982f1b022bd7ea9d7","tid":543488,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-28T14:27:53.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://assets.post852.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/01/28130702/image1517115855529.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fassets.post852.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2018%2F01%2F28130702%2Fimage1517115855529.png&h=13a5385d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n政務司司長張建宗今日再回應香港眾志常委周庭被撤銷參選資格一事，重申選舉主任是政治中立及不偏不倚，DQ周庭的理由清晰，且已作清楚交代，政府支持選舉主任之工作和決定，但指政府不宜評論個別個案，因往後可能會有法律訴訟。他續指，如周庭不接受被DQ，可提出選舉呈請，又補充稱，《基本法》列明香港市民享有參選及被選的權利，但同時要平衡合乎《基本法》及一國兩制之要求。<br />\n<br />\n2016的立法會換屆選舉，時任本土民主前線發言人梁天琦和社民連主席吳文遠等，就確認書與選舉主任法定權力等問題，提請司法覆核，但高院法官區慶祥認為案件沒急切性，決定不批准緊急處理，只會依循正常程序，不會在後日選舉提名截止日前裁決。<br />\n<br />\n香港民族黨召集人陳浩天及梁天琦最終同被撤參選資格，二人其後分別在9月及10月入稟高院提出選舉呈請，質疑選舉主任的權力，及選舉主任的相關決定非法與違憲。不過陳浩天案在去年5月審結後，仍未公布裁決，梁天琦之呈請更有待法庭處理。"},{"pid":"75736d06706c6f800b8db77b83055b06dc5abc82","tid":543488,"uid":101392,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-28T16:06:18.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/542503/page/2\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/542503/page/2</a><br />\n<br />\n法庭成日扮曬中立 一睇案件排期好明顯大細超啦<br />\n政府DQ六個議員就光速審完<br />\n參選人選舉呈請就拖到任期就完都唔審<br />\n搵人質問下馬道立啦"},{"pid":"e8319baecc75f43a6cff94682c8f42a61d2e9c2b","tid":543488,"uid":153689,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-28T16:10:13.000Z","msg":"屌你老母同何君堯講嘅嘢一鳩樣"},{"pid":"8bde77cbb4ee755d14f22a945cde14e66ace2201","tid":543488,"uid":130105,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"75736d06706c6f800b8db77b83055b06dc5abc82","tid":543488,"uid":101392,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-28T16:06:18.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/542503/page/2\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/542503/page/2</a><br />\n<br />\n法庭成日扮曬中立 一睇案件排期好明顯大細超啦<br />\n政府DQ六個議員就光速審完<br />\n參選人選舉呈請就拖到任期就完都唔審<br />\n搵人質問下馬道立啦"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-28T16:27:14.000Z","msg":"做樣嘛<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/37.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5873f15754fcc21b05482d20c3e0d0a4e0952642","tid":543488,"uid":14918,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-28T16:37:05.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://www.azquotes.com/picture-quotes/quote-justice-too-long-delayed-is-justice-denied-martin-luther-king-87-68-87.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.azquotes.com%2Fpicture-quotes%2Fquote-justice-too-long-delayed-is-justice-denied-martin-luther-king-87-68-87.jpg&h=45d093f6&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"79bbaa69c1789153d25f1a82441f5f74c194c647","tid":543488,"uid":20561,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-28T17:25:21.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"97954b30672bd1bc9bb035a2337d320362268b71","tid":543488,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-29T03:18:47.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}